                "articleOutId": "61432f2c2b08423f84fd7c06d24497c7",
                "html": "<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">Andy Ferguson</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">Andy \"Icky\" Ferguson is a self-proclaimed Limited fanatic, with his first draft in 1999 at the age of 11. Over two decades later, you can still find him at the Draft tables, coaching, and occasionally streaming, always with the motto: \"Lose and learn, learn and win.\" In 2021, he was the #1 Limited player on MTG Arena for five out of twelve months.</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">Ten Bloomburrow Combos And Synergies For Limited Magic</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">With Arena Open: Bloomburrow coming up this weekend, here are ten common and uncommon combos and synergies you need to know for Bloomburrow’s Limited formats.</p> \n<ol data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 25px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> \n <li> \n  <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(1, 1, 1); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n    Harvestrite Host + Intrepid Rabbit // Hop to It // Head of the Homestead \n  </section></li> \n</ol> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">Harvestrite Host Intrepid Rabbit Hop to It Head of the Homestead</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">Not only is Harvestrite Host’s second sentence incredibly strong, Bloomburrow Limited has an abundance of cards that will let you draw free cards. You can always cast an additional Rabbit in the same turn, or bust out the Carrot Cake like any good host should!</p> \n<ol start=\"2\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 25px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> \n <li> \n  <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(1, 1, 1); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n    Cache Grab + Eddymurk Crab \n  </section></li> \n</ol> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">Cache Grab Eddymurk Crab</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">Two cards not commonly paired together, but powerful when built around. Cache Grab is incredibly efficient at filling up your graveyard, while pulling the Eddymurk Crab out of the proverbial sand.</p> \n<ol start=\"3\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 25px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> \n <li> \n  <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(1, 1, 1); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n    Shore Up + Tempest Angler \n  </section></li> \n</ol> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">Shore Up Tempest Angler</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">If your deck uses Tempest Angler as its win condition, this is a common Turn 4 play, keeping up Shore Up the rest of the game as the Angler grows.</p> \n<ol start=\"4\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 25px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> \n <li> \n  <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(1, 1, 1); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n    Stormcatch Mentor + Pearl of Wisdom \n  </section></li> \n</ol> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">Stormcatch Mentor Pearl of Wisdom</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">Though Stormcatch Mentor hasn’t performed all that well from what I’ve seen, paying one mana for a draw-two is still pretty sweet.</p> \n<ol start=\"5\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 25px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> \n <li> \n  <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(1, 1, 1); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n    Splash Portal + Pond Prophet \n  </section></li> \n</ol> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">Splash Portal Pond Prophet</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">On the topic of the one-mana draw two, here’s another nice option to do so. Daring Waverider is also worth mentioning, as you can draw a free card if Splash Portal is in your graveyard when you cast it!</p> \n<ol start=\"6\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 25px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> \n <li> \n  <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(1, 1, 1); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n    Moonstone Harbinger + Moonrise Cleric // Lifecreed Duo \n  </section></li> \n</ol> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">Moonstone Harbinger Moonrise Cleric Lifecreed Duo</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">Both Moonrise Cleric and Lifecreed Duo are nice pairings for Moonstone Harbinger, with Lifecreed Duo lining up as a quality Turns 2-3 sequence, but requiring a creature each turn for the trigger.</p> \n<ol start=\"7\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 25px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> \n <li> \n  <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(1, 1, 1); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n    Seasoned Warrenguard + Carrot Cake \n  </section></li> \n</ol> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">Seasoned Warrenguard Carrot Cake</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">This Turns 1-2 sequence nets you a 3/2 attacker on Turn 2. Really gives me some Wild Nacatl vibes.</p> \n<ol start=\"8\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 25px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> \n <li> \n  <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(1, 1, 1); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n    Heartfire Hero + Feather of Flight Heartfire Hero Feather of Flight \n  </section></li> \n</ol> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">A strong Boros opener, this duo provides you an attacking 3/2 flyer on Turn 2 that Lightning Bolts your opponent when it dies.</p> \n<ol start=\"9\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 25px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> \n <li> \n  <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(1, 1, 1); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n    Agate-Blade Assassin + Scales of Shale \n  </section></li> \n</ol> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">Agate-Blade Assassin Scales of Shale</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">To be fair, Scales of Shale has a ton of great applications, but the pairing with Agate-Blade Assassin was a good one to highlight because of the Lizard synergy, and the Assassin wants to attack each turn, allowing you to trade-up easily.</p> \n<ol start=\"10\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 25px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> \n <li> \n  <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(1, 1, 1); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n    Shrike Force + Treeguard Duo \n  </section></li> \n</ol> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">Shrike Force Treeguard Duo</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">A strong combination to end the game out of nowhere, as well as a perfectly fine sequence on Turns 3-4 to dish out some solid damage.</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">Keep these combos, and one could help you win some money in the Arena Open!</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">Lose and Learn, Learn and Win!</p>",
